  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to determine the effetiveness of the intensive upper and lower limbs
      therapy to improve the funtional outcomes and to minimize ther energetic spendings during
      funtional activities in Cerebral Palsy patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to determine the effetiveness of the intensive upper and lower limbs
      therapy to improve the funtional outcomes and to minimize ther energetic spendings during
      funtional activities in Cerebral Palsy patients. Also to know paretns and caregivers
      perceptions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
